com.ephesoft.dcma.imagemagick

Class MultiPageExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ephesoft.dcma.imagemagick.MultiPageExecutor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICommonConstants, ImageMagicKConstants

    public class MultiPageExecutor
extends java.lang.Object
implements ImageMagicKConstants, ICommonConstants
    Class is used for creating multipage tiff and pdf using ImageMagik, GhostScript and iText. This class provides functionalities that process single page tiff files using ImageMagik, GhostScript and iText and create multipage file corresponding to single page tiff files.

        public MultiPageExecutor(BatchInstanceThread batchInstanceThread,
                 java.util.Map<java.lang.String,HocrPages.HocrPage> imageHocrMap,
                 boolean isColoredPDF,

                 java.lang.String pdfFilePath,
                 java.lang.String[] pages,
                 java.lang.String fontFilePath,
                 java.lang.String convertParameters,
                 java.lang.String iTextSearchablePDFType)
        The MultiPageExecutor method creates multi page searchable pdf using IText.
        Parameters:
        batchInstanceThread - BatchInstanceThread thread instance of batch.
        imageHtmlMap - Map map containing image url with corresponding hocr.
        isColoredPDF - true for colored image pdf else otherwise.
        isSearchablePDF - true for searchable pdf else otherwise.
        pdfFilePath - String path where new pdf has to be created.
        pages - String[] is the imageUrl
        fontFilePath - String specifies the path of font file.
        convertParameters - String specifying the convert command parameters for the image before iText pdf creation.
        iTextSearchablePDFType - String IText searchable pdf type (Pdf or pdf Advanced).
